<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- sayĩdī naf̊siy̱ ladaẙk̊
 ʿin̊da maẘṭī̊̉ qadamaẙk̊
 waḥayātī fī yadaẙk̊
 fah̊ya min̊ka wāi̹laẙk̊

[C1]
   ạlqrạr- sayĩdī mādẖā turīd̊
   ạih̊dinī ḥaẙtẖu turīd̊
   ại̹nãnī las̊tu ạủrīd̊
   gẖaẙra fiʿ̊li mā turīd̊

[V2]
 2- rabĩy̱ hab̊niy̱ ạản̊ ạảrāk̊
 kaẙ ạảsīra fiy̱ kẖuṭāk̊
 ạản̊ta rabĩy̱ lạ siwāk̊
 bugẖ̊yatiy̱ naẙlu riḍāk̊

[V3]
 3- bạltqy̱ wbạlkẖsẖwʿ
 bạtḍạʿiⁿ wkẖḍwʿ
 wbqlb lạ yrwʿ
 ạ̉ʿbd ạlrb yswʿ</lyrics>
